items.title: Israel and Hamas Agree Another Hostage Release and Prisoner Exchange
items.description: The remains of four Israeli hostages will be turned over in exchange for hundreds of Palestinian prisoners whose release had been delayed.

items.title: Wildfire Burning on Table Mountain Moves Toward Cape Town
items.description: Firefighters have battled a blaze on the slopes in the national park for days. The fire spread overnight toward Cape Town’s central business district.
